title: Olde Mill Inn Tour of Basking Ridge
North Cross
description: North Cross Cyclocross Races are part of the NJBA CX Cup Series.
course: The course is approx. 1.4miles in length with tight turns, elevation gains, and a barrier section.
registration:
DAY OF RACE REGISTRATION (+$10.00) WILL BE ACCEPTED
 PRE-REGISTRATION IS STRONGLY SUGGESTED.


If you are registering for 2 classes, the second class registration fee will be $15 - however, you must register for the 2nd class at the race, as BikeReg can\'t discount a second class. No penalty for onsite registration of second class. Mountain bikes are ok for all races, no bar ends. Mountain bike license\'s are ok for all races.


Late fee $10 day of registration does not apply to U19.  Must have valid USCF license to participate. One day license available day of race for $10 additional fee. Must have drivers license, birth certificate or valid passport to purchase.
notes: Prize list based on min. 30 entrants per field. We reserve the right to combine fields with fewer than fifteen entrants.
directions: Race is held at Highlands Ridge Park in Chester, NJ on County Road 510.
